&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own Compensation Operations&lt;/strong&gt; - Run compensation operations for geo-transfers, role transfers, promotions, recognition programs, and other ad-hoc needs. Contribute to job architecture decisions as our business evolves.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Offer Negotiation Strategy&lt;/strong&gt; - Partner with Recruiting and Finance to enhance our offer compensation strategy that ensures we continue to win top talent at a sustainable cost.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Insights through People Analytics&lt;/strong&gt; - Identify where decisions could be helped with more data, and then provide that data in simple and accurate ways. More generally, ensure we&#39;re utilizing our existing infrastructure, systems, and tools to the best of our ability. Advocate for and drive improvements where possible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contribute to Operational Excellence&lt;/strong&gt; - Contribute to the team&#39;s broader operational excellence in your day-to-day work. Create automated audits and other checks to ensure data integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
