&lt;li&gt;Mission-first, user-first attitude and approach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear and direct communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical skills (in Google Sheets or similar) that will allow you to independently run compensation programs and operations, turn data into insights, and separate signal from noise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced analytical skills (in SQL or similar) that enable you to build dashboards and automated reporting for the compensation function and the broader People Team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Well-organized with high attention to detail, ensuring compensation data is always correct.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
