&lt;li&gt;Drive alignment on scope and timelines, across internal and external stakeholders, with technical and non-technical background, balancing technical feasibility with risk management and high-quality outcomes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively monitor existing production systems and drive root-cause analysis and resolution on likely high-severity customer issues, before they impact production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and maintain high-quality software while guiding customers to apply Intrinsic’s products effectively.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a bridge between customers and internal teams, especially to shape our product roadmap and to serve as a senior escalation point for APAC customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a bridge to global leadership, especially by proactively identifying and raising areas in which refinements in our strategy are needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and grow the regional Customer Success engineering team, especially by cultivating team motivation through clear communication, providing the &quot;why&quot; and &quot;how&quot; behind strategic changes and regional decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
