&lt;li&gt;2 years of experience in robotics software development or simulation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency programming in C++ and Python.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with the Gazebo simulator and ROS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with physics engines (e.g., Dart, Bullet, ODE, MuJoCo).&lt;/li&gt;
